INkqubo eyaziwa njengeWaste Wise
ISixeko saseKapa siqalise iNkqubo eyaziwa njengeWaste Wise ngowama-2002 ukunceda ukunciphisa
inkunkuma, ukulahla okokungekho mthethweni, nongcoliseko eKapa.
Injongo ephambili yale nkqubo
kukufundisa abemi baseKapa malunga nenyaniso kunye neziphumo zenkunkuma, ze ekugqibeleni libonise
abantu ngendlela abangaba yinxalenye ngayo ekwenzeni kwabo okuncinanana ukukhusela indalo.
Ngowama-2006, iKapa libe sesinye sezixeko eAfrika ukumilisela isiCwangciso esiHlangeneyo soLawulo
lweNkunkuma.
Enye yeenjongo ezingundoqo zesi zicwangciso kukunciphisa umthamo wenkunkuma
othunyelwa kwiitiphu zaseKapa ngaphezulu kwama-25% kwiminyaka embalwa elandelayo.
Ukulungiselela
ukufezekisa le njongo ngama-2012, iSixeko sidinga ukuphuhlisa nokuqalisa ngeenkqubo ezisebenzayo
Ukufundisa abemi bexa elizayo baseKapa
Enye yenkqutyana engundoqo yeNkqubo eyaziwa njengeWaste Wise kukuphuhlisa nokumilisela
ukufundisa okusebenzayo kunye nenkqubo nokuguqulwa kwezinto ebezisetyenzisiwe eziyinkunkuma
ziphinde zisebenze kwakhona elungiselelwe izikolo eKapa.
Iinjongo zale nkqubo zezi: •
• Ukuphakamisa iqondo lolwazi kubafundisi-ntsapho, abafundi kunye neentsapho zabo.
Ukuncedisa abafundisi-ntsapho baphakamise iqondo lolwazi lwabo ngentsusa nefuthe lolawulo
olungasebenziyo lwenkunkuma kunye nezibonelelo zolawulo oluhlanganisiweyo lwenkunkuma.
Ukunikezela ngezixhobo zendalo ukwandisa ubume bempilo babemi baseKapa.
Ukunceda izikolo ngokuphuhlisa ipotfoliyo kunye neeprojekti zokunciphisa inkunkuma. • •
Ukuza kuthi ga ngoku, izikolo ezili-100 eKapa zithabathe inxaxheba kwiNkqubo yeZikolo eyaziwa
njengeWasteWise yaye ngoncedo lwale ncwadana, sinethemba lokokuba isikolo sakho siya kuba
sesinye esibandakanyekayo. Le ncwadana iya kukunika lonke ulwazi ngokunjalo namacebo asebenzayo
kunye nengcebiso oya kuyidinga ukuqalisa nokulawula ulawulo lwenkunkuma oluyimpumelelo kunye
kwisikolo sakho.
Sikunqwenelela impumelelo, siqinisekile uya kulifumana eli galelo likunika umdla yaye
likwanelisa.
