UKUNCIPHISA INKUNKUMA
EVELISWA SISIKOLO
Eyona ndlela ilungileyo yokusombulula ingxaki
yenkunkuma eKapa kukunciphisa umthamo wenkunkuma
oveliswayo.
Kuxhonyekekwe kwisiphumo sophengululo
lwenkunkuma, isikolo sakho kufuneka sizame yaye sinike
ingqwalasela kwimithombo yenkunkuma oyivelisa kakhulu.
Nanga amacebo okunciphisa inkunkuma oyivelisayo:
• Thintela ukuthenga iimveliso ezisongelwe ngezinto
ezininzi.
• Nciphisa usongelo oluninzi ngokuthenga kakhulu
ngexesha elinye izinto ozisebenzisa rhoqo
nangokuthenga izinto onokuphinda uzizalise kwakhona
• Zama ukuthenga iimveliso ezinezisongelo ezenziwe
yasebenza kwakhona.
• Zama ukuba ungathengi iimveliso ozisebenzisa
oyisebenzisa uyilahle okanye iipleyiti
• Khetha iglasi ngaphezulu kweplastiki njengoko
Uninzi
lweiznto zokusongela zeplastiki azikwazi
ukuguqulwa ukuze ziphinde zisetyenziswe
• Zinxweme zonke iimveliso ezinetyhefu
neziyingozi. Umzekelo, zama ukusebenzisa
iimveliso zokucoc zezinto eziphilayo kwisikolo
sakho nasekhaya. Zikhuselekile noko kuwe
nakwindalo.
Ingcamango!
Kutheni ungabeli indawo
yokuvelisa inkunkuma kwiklasi nganye kwisikolo
sakho ze ucele abafundi ukuba mabeze neendlela
ezihlakaniphileyo zokunciphisa umthamo
wenkunkuma oveliswayo.
Milisela iingcamango
ezisebenzayo ze ulandele ifuthe ezithe zanalo
ekuvelisweni kwenkunkuma.
Vuza iklasi ezithe
iingcebiso zayo zanefuthe elikhulu kumthamo
wenkunkuma oveliswa sisikolo.
