Ukulungiselela
iiplastiki, uya kudinga amabhali eengxowa,
yaye ngokufanelekileyo, indawo yokuxhoma
ezo ngxowa.
Ezi ndawo zokuxhoma
zixhasa iingxowa zaye ziqinisekisa ngento
yokuba zihlala zivulekile, into eyenza kuba
lula ukulahla kuzo inkunkuma ehleliweyo
nokukhangela into yokokuba udidi olunye
lweplastiki lugcinwa kunye.
Qinisekisa ngento
yokuba amabhali eengxowa alebhelishwe
ngokucacileyo (umz. PET 1 okanye PET 4)
ukunceda abahleli ngendawo apho udidi
