LWEXESHA ELIDE
Impumelelo yethuba elide yenkqubo yolawulo
yokuguqulwa kwenkunkuma iya kuxhomekeka
ekuqondeni nasekuqapheleni ukuba uyila yaye
uzibophelela ixesha elide ekubeni le nto isebenze.
Ngawo la ke amanye amacebiso anxulumene
nokumiselwa nokuyila le nkqubo, ufundisa abantu
ngendlela eza kusebenzayo ngayo nokugcina le
nkqubo isoloko iqhubeka:
Ukuvelisa ulwazi
Ngokubanzi
• Uguquguquko lwenkunkuma malubonwe
njengento eyonwabisayo nelula. Khawucinge
ngokuququzelela ukuyila umsitho ovuyisayo
noza kubandakanya isikolo sonke, abazali, am-
alunga aphambili oluntu ekuhlaleni, amashishini
(asele enikeze ngenkxaso kweli phulo okanye
wena onqwenela ukugaya inkxaso yawo) kunye
nabezosasazo (imidiya) engingqini.
Kwabasebenzi
• Bamba intlanganiso yokwazisa
abasebenzi oku kubandakanya kunye
nabasebenzi abacocayo.
• Bacacisele unobangela wokuba isikolo sifuna
ukumilisela inkqubo yolawulo lokuguqulwa
kwenkunkuma kwakunye nendlela le
nkqubo isebenza ngayo.
Cacisa indima ema
idlalwe nguye wonke umntu ukuqinisekisa
ukuphumelela kweli linge.
• Qhuba iseshoni yocweyo yabasebenzi
Qinisekisa
ukuba onke amalungu angabasebenzi
ayayiqondi le nkqubo – ukususela kubala
lwenkunkuma engenayo. Ukuququzelela
kukuqokelelwa ngaphakathi nangaphandle
ngendima ema idlalwe lilungu ngalinye
kubasebenzi.
• Yile ikhalenda ebonisa imihla ebalulelileyo
emalunga neprogramu kwibhodi yezaziso
yabasebenzi.
• Qhuba ngeeseshoni zoqeqesho ezilandelayo
ukunika abasebenzi iingcinga nengqondo
ngendlela yokuquka amanqaku/imiba
ngolawulo lwenkunkuma kwikharityhulam.
Phakathi kwabafundi
• Yenza ukuba abafundi abangamalungu ekomiti
solawulo lwenkunkuma ngethuba kumiwe
emgceni kusasa kwi-asembli.
Cinga ngeendlela
zokuyenza le nkcazelo ibe nomdla, ihlwabise
idale nengxoko.
• Nika inkcazelo ngokuqhubekayo rhoqo
ngeeveki ezimbini uchazele abafundi
ngokuqhubekayo kwinkqubo.
Bonisa
iziganeko eziphambili kunye nempumelelo,
konke oku kwibhodi yezaziso nakwiwebhsayithi
• Cinga ngokququzelela imisebenzi yoluntu
emalunga nolawulo lwenkunkuma, efana
neentsuku zokucoca koluntu kwasekuhlaleni
nalapho abafundi bephuma baye eluntwini
bancedise ekuqokelelweni kwenkunkuma.
• Nika abafundi ifaskothi esibhaliweyo
okanye iminqwazi bathwale ngezo ntsuku
kuqokelelwa inkunkuma kwiindawo zoguqulo
• Ququzelela utyelelo lwelungu lukamasipala
wakho lesebe lezolawulo lwenkunkuma.
Phakathi kwabazali
• Landelisa esi siganeko sokumiselwa ngokuthumela emakhaya isikhokelo
esimalunga “Nendlela yokuguqula inkunkuma” esithunyelwa kubo
bonke abazali.
Esi sikhokelo masicacise ngokuzeleyo ngezo zinto abazali
banokuzithumela nazo bangenakho ukuzithumela kwiziko lesikolo
lokuguqula inkunkuma.
Kwakhona nendlela yokuthumela ezo zinto –
umzekelo, zihlanjwe kukhutshwe onke amanzi, njalo njalo.
• Cela uMbutho waBazali uquke iprogramu yolawulo lwenkunkuma
njengenye yemiba yokufakwa kwi-ajenda yeentlanganiso.
• Quka rhoqo okuqhubekayo malunga nolawulo lwenkunkuma ngemiba
yokwenziweyo namalinge amatsha acetywayo – konke oku kufakwe
kwincwadana yesikolo.
• Cela kubazali abanokuba namacebo neengcamango zokuphucula
iprogramu okanye zokugaya inkxaso-mali kusenzelwa ilinge badibane
nekomiti yolawulo lwenkunkuma.
Ukuqhubela phambili
Kukodwa ukuqalisa ngenkqubo yesikolo
yokuguqula inkunkuma logama ungomnye
umcimbi nonzima ukuqhubela phambili ngaloo
nkqubo.
Eli candela lilandelayo likunika amacebo
anokusetyenziswa nasebenzayo mlaunga
nokuqinisekisa ukuba ihlala isisigxina loo nkqubo.
• Qinisekisa ukuba unelungu elungumsebenzi
eliyintshatsheli kumba wenkunkuma – ubani
olithathele kuye uxanduva lokuthundeza
nokuqhubela phambili ngenkqubo leyo.
Qinisekisa ukuba intshatsheli le isoloko iyibeke
esweni le nkqubo yaye ibonelela ngengxelo
kwikomiti ejongene nomba wenkunkuma.
Intshatsheli le kufuneka kwakhona ichazele
intloko yezemfundo kunye nabo bonke
abasebenzi ngokuqhubekayo kwixesha elinye
ngokunxulumene nokuhambela phambili
kwenkqubo kwakunye namanye amalinge
azayo. • Ukubeka imiqathango eqinisekisa ukusoloko
usiva ingxelo kubantu abalawula iziko
lokuguqula inkunkuma.
Baza kuba nolwazi
olucacileyo malunga nobungakanani (volume)
benkunkuma efikayo/engenayo nendlela
eguqulwa ngayo.
baza kukwazi ukukulumkisa khon’ ukuze
ukwazi ukubeka imiqathango yokukhuthaza
kwakhona abafundi, abazali, abasebenzi
kunye nabacoci.
Abasebenzi beziko nabo
basenokukulumkisa malunga naziphi na
iingxaki ezifunyanwa yiprogramu.
• Ukuba izinga lokuthatha inxaxheba
imiba enxulumeneyo ephathelele kulawulo
lwenkunkuma kwizicwangciso zezifundo.
Cinga ngeehambo zotyelelo ngezemfundo
ukunika abafundi ithuba lokuzibonela
ngokwabo iindawo zokulahla inkunkuma.
Okanye umeme/ubize iingcali zize kuthetha
nabafundi malunga nenkunkuma kwakunye
nempembelelo enayo kokusingqongileyo.
• Sibuyekeze isikolo ngenkqubo yaso
enempumelelo – wonke umntu uyayifuna
ingqalelo xa enempumelelo.
Thetha
nabezosasazo malunga nenkqubo
nokwenziweyo ngempumelelo ikhangele ukuba
oko akunakupapashwa na.
Seka imbuyekezo
ngemali elungiselelwe iintshatsheli zolawulo
lwenkunkuma – iklasi eza nelona cebo nendlela
yokuphinda isetyenziswe inkunkuma okanye
iklasi eyila/ezoba ezona powusta zitsala zidale
ingqalelo ngenkunkuma kusenzelwa iziko
lesikolo lokuguqula inkunkuma.
Kwakhona,
• Okokugqibela, qwalasela isicwangciso
sokulandelelana. Oku kukuqinisekisa ukuba
le nkqubo yolawulo lwenkunkuma aluwi
phantsi zakuba iintshatsheli zezenkunkuma
zisishiyile isikolo, sebenzisa isicwangciso
secebo sokulandelalana.
Umzekelo, kuya
kusoloko kukho umbutho wabazali, ke ngoko
banike umsebenzi wokunyula abazali ababini
abaya kuba sekomitini yolawulo lwenkunkuma
rhoqo ngonyaka ngamnye.
Okanye uqinisekise
ukuba utitshala oyintloko wonyula intshatsheli
yenkunkuma phakathi kweqela labasebenzi
oko kusenziwa ngonyaka ngamnye.
Umsebenzi wokuqwalasela iprogramu yolawulo
lwenkunkumaq ibe yinxalenye yomsebenzi
wakho kuloo nyaka.
IMIBA ENGUNDOQO UKULUNGISELELA IMPUMELELO
Kuyo yonke le ncwadana sixoxe ngemiba eliqela
engundoqo ekubeni isikolo sakho siseke yaye
siqhube ngenkqubo yolawulo lwenkunkuma.
Nasi isishwankathelo sazo zonke iibhokisi
ekufuneka zibekwe uphawu ukuqinisekisa ukuba
ilinge/iphulo lakho liya kuba nempumelelo.
• Abantu bokuqaqambisa bavakalisa
ukulahlwa kwenkunkuma okungekho
mthethweni kwakhona nokuthintela
abantu ekubeni babe inkunkuma esele
ihleliwe.
Ukwafuna iindawo ezinezalathiso
ezichaza iindidi zenkunkuma kwisikolo
sonke ukuqinisekisa ukuba kulula ukuguqula
inkunkuma njengoko kukwanjalo xa uyilahla.
• Abasebenzi bokuguqula inkunkuma
injongo – qinisekisa ukuba usoloko
unentshatsheli yenkunkuma ehleli ikho,
ekhatshwa linani lamatshantliziyo azimiseleyo
ajongene nenkunkuma.
• Inkxaso esuka ngasentla – qiniseka
ukuba amalungu angabalawuli abaphezulu
besikolo ayayiqonda yaye eyixhasa inkqubo
yolawulo lwenkunkuma.
Le mayithathwe
njengenxalenye yemisebenzi eyinkqubo
yesikolo imihla ngemihla.
• Inkxaso evela kubasebenzi – sebenzela
ukuba icandelo, unogada wesikolo kunye
nabasebenzi abacocayo bayayiqonda beyixhasa
le nkqubo yolawulo lwenkunkuma.
• Iindawo zokuguqulwa kwenkunkuma
– ukuba nezibonelelo zokusebenza kunye
nezixhobo kungundoqo, kubalulekile.
Kufuneka
ufumane ummandla okhuselekileyo, odibeneyo
yaye ukhuselwe nalapho uza kuqhuba
khona umsebenzi wokuguqula inkunkuma.
Makungabikho ndlela yakungena ngethuba
leeyure ezingezizo zesikolo, oku kukunqanda
– iziko lakho liza kufuna abantu bokulisebenza
ngokuhamba kwamaxesha.
Amavolontiya
akholisa ukungathembeki kunabasebenzi
abazuza umvuzo, ke ngoko zama ukufuna
iindlela zokugaya nokunyusa ingxowa-mali
ukuze kuqeshwe abasebenzi.
Khumbula ukuba
kuza kufuneka ufune umntu onezakhono
khon’ ukuze uzuze amathuba neemeko ezona
zingcono kubanikezeli ngeenkonzo, abaqokeleli
kunye nabaguquli benkunkuma.
• Ukukwazi ukudala ulwazi nokuqonda
abafundi, kunye nabazali bayayazi inkqubo
yolawulo lwenkunkuma, izibonelelo
beyenzile.
Uthethwano lubalulekile
ukugcina la maqela angundoqo enolwazi
oluhlaziywayo qho ngenqubela yenkqubo noko
kucwangciselwe inqanaba eliladelayo.
