kwaye aya kulawulwa ngokufanelekileyo.
• Ukulondoloza imeko-bume ecocekileyo engaselunxwemeni luxanduva ekwabelwana ngalo
phakathi kwamasebe eSixeko, imibutho yangaphandle nabasebenzisi beelwandle
abazimeleyo. Okona kubalulekileyo kuMgaqo-nkqubo wokuCocwa kweeNdawo ezingaseluNxwemeni yinkcazelo
yenkunkuma yeSixeko.
