apho sithi silungise imithetho yangaphambili engocalu-calulo lweentlanga, silungise
ukungalingani okukhoyo kunikezelo lophuhliso lweendawo zokuhlala ezahlukeneyo, kwakhona
Sithi sithathe
ezothutho njengomqhubi ophambili ekulungiseni ubume obububo bezamabala baseKapa
kwaye sijolise ekufezekiseni inguqu kezamabala ngokuthi sisebenzise uphuhliso olujoliswe
kwezothutho (TOD) nokungunganiswa kwezakhiwo okunxulumene noko.
ISicwangciso esiluYilo sezoThutho ngokuBanzi esiHlangeneyo, sango-2017 ukuya ngo-2022 (CITP), siscwangciso esitsha
ngokusemthethweni, esiqulunqwe ngokwecandelo-36 (1) loMthetho weSizwe ongezoThutho ezihamba eMhlabeni ongunomb.5 wango-2009.
Isicwangciso sithi singqinelane nexesha elitsha lokusebenza kwe-IDP yango-2017 ukuya
ngo-2022, kwaye ithi ihlangane neSakheko esiphengululilweyo soPhuhliso lomhlaba ongamaBala sikaMasipala.
Umxholo nesakheko se-CITP uthi ukhokelwe yiGazethi yasebuRhulumenteni engunomb.40174 yowama-29 kweyeKhala 2016
apho sithi sivakalise “Umlinganiselo ofunekayo ngokumalunga namaLungiselelo eziCwangciso eziHlangeneyo zezoThutho”.
Isicwangciso esiBanzi sezoThutho ngokuHlangeneyo (CITP) sithi sinike iSixeko saseKapa (uGunyaziwe ongezoThutho,
uGunyaziwe ongezoThutho noPhuhliso lweDolophu waseKapa (TDA), igunya laso elijoliswe kuthungelwano lwezothutho
nayo yonke into ethi ihambelane nalo.
Kwesi Sicwangciso sitsha se-CITP, iSixeko saseKapa sithi siqulunqe indlela apho siyakuthi inkqubela siyandise ngayo, ethe
olutshintshiselanayo ngokwezixhobo.
Ukuthathelwa kwengqalelo kwecandelo ngalinye:
• Ehlangeneyo: Unikezelo lweSixeko lezothutho oluhlangeneyo lubhekiselele kwiSicwangciso saso sezoThungelwano
“Uhlangeneyo” ke ngoko, akufunekanga nje usuke
uphelele/ujoliswe kuphela kwezothutho kodwa kufuneka kwakhona uthethe ukuhlanganiswa kwezothutho kunye
nokusetyenziswa komhlaba.
NgokweSixeko, oku kuthetha ukusetyenziswa kophuhliso olujoliswe kwezothutho (TOD)
ukuze kufezekiswe inguqu kumabala kubuqu beKapa kunye nakwakhiwa koluntu lasekuhlaleni oluluqilima.
kokuba yonke imisebenzi neentlobo zothutho ziphantsi kwemida yolawulo lukagunyaziwe omnye.
Ukuza kuthi ga
ngoku, iSixeko siqhubekeka ngokusebenzisa imisebenzi kaGunyaziwe ongeKhontrakthi nemisebenzi yeQumrhu
leGunya likaMasipala (MRE), ngokulandelelana.
Kwakhona iSixeko siyakwamkela ukuba nangona ezothutho
lukaloliwe “lulelona lungundoqo” kwinkqubo yaso yezothutho, kodwa ke ngokunje lusengxakini.
ISixeko ke ngoko
sithathela ingqalelo indlela esiyakuthi sijongane ngayo nale ngxaki eKapa.
• Uhlobo olutshintshiselanayo ngokwezixhobo: Ukuze kufezekiswe inkqubo eluhlobo olutshintshiselanayo ngezixhobo
(apho inkqubo yezothutho ethile enakho ukusebenza kunye nenye kungakhange kwenziwe iinzame ezizodwa
ngokujoliswe kubakhweli), iSixeko siyakuthi sibenakho ukuqhuba umsebenzi othe xhaxhe ngokumalunga
nokunikezelwa kwamatikiti namaxesha okuhamba kwezithuthi ngokuhlangeneyo.
Indlela ethile iSixeko esijolise kuyo kwezothutho oluhlangeneyo kukuba simisele iintlobo ngeentlobo ezingezothutho.
Iintlobo eziphambili zezenkonzo kaloliwe, uhlobo oluthile lweebhasi ezihamba ngokukhawuleza (BRT), iinkonzo zebhasi
kuthungelwano ngokubanzi nala lisebenza ngokumandla kwezothutho oluxubeneyo) nakwiiteksi ezizikhumbi ezincinane.
Ezi ntlobo zothutho ziyakuthi kunye zenze inxal’enye yesisombululo sezothutho oluhlangeneyo apho luyakuthi lumiselwe
kwiinkulungwane ezizayo kwaye kuyakuba ngumphumela “wesizukulwana esitsha” kunikezelo lwenkonzo.
Indlela ethile yeSixeko ngokujoliswe kuPhuhliso olujoliswe kwezoThutho (TOD)
apho indlela iSixeko esiyakuthi sijolise kuyo ukusebenzisa ezothutho ukuze kutshintshwe isimo samabala kwiKapa
ubuqu kunye nokwakha uluntu lwasekuhlaleni oluluqilima.
Oku kuthetha ukuba iSixeko asijolisanga kuphela
ekufezekiseni ezothutho oluhlanganisiweyo.
Endaweni yoko ikuthatha ezothutho njengomqhubi ophambili
ekulungisweni kwemeko ekukuyo yamabala aseKapa, kunye nayo yonke imibandela eyimiqobo yedolophu
nokungalingani ngokwentlalo.
