nakwiKapa.
Impendulo koku, isicwangciso-buchule kwezothutho eKapa saye sajolisa kulwandiso lothungelwano zokuhamba-hamba
kwabasebenzisi bezithuthi zabucala, kwaye nokwanda kweedolophana. Ukwanda kothungelwano
lwendlela nokwanda kweedolophana (kokungena edolophini) kuye kwangumphumela koluntu
olwahlulwa-hluliweyo kwaye
iindawo ezininzi ziye zawunikela umva umbandela wokuhamba ngebhayisekile nongummiselo onokusebenza nokhuselekileyo. Ngenxa yoko ke, kwaye yehla
lohambo ngeebhayisekile
iihambo zorhoqo ngemini ezenziwe zathelekiswa
nokusetyenziswa kwezinye iindlela zezothutho) ukususela ngoo-1980 kwakhona kuye kwehla
abafundi abakhwela ibhayisekile xa besiya esikolweni.
Inguqulelo entsha eyenzeke kwihlabathi nokukhula koluntu oluhamba ngeebhayisekile kuye
kuhlonitshwa ngakumbi njengegalelo elibalulekileyo kwizixeko ezijolise kwindumasi nobuqilima.
ISixeko saseKapa ekubeni siye sakwamkela ukuba ukuhamba ngebhayisekile kuye kwanda ukuba
kubeyinxal’enye ebalulekileyo yesisombululo kwezothutho, siye saqalisa ukuqulunqa iSicwangciso-
buchule esingokuhamba ngebhayisekile.
elohlukeneyo oluvela kwabo bachaphazelekayo basebenzisa ihambo ngebhayisekile ngenjongo
