Uphengululo okanye uphando olujoliswe kwizixeko eziphumeleleyo kwezohambo ngebhayisekile luye
iKapa yindlela yokwandisa ukukhwela ukhuselo nokhuseleko, kubonelelwe
kuphuculwe linabo ubunganga bokukhulisa
iihambo zeebhaysekile ngokuluncedo kwaye ulikhulise, kufuneka kuqhutywe inkqubo enxaxhileyo engohambo ngebhayisekile. Iinkalo
eziphambili ekujoliswe kuzo ezicwangcisiweyo ngethuba lokuqulunqwa kwesi sicwangciso-buchule
esingohambo ngebhayisekile ukuba kukhuthazwe kwaye kukhuliswe inkonzo yoncedo kuhambo
ngebhayisekile lubonakalise indlela ethile ngokubanzi kwaye iquka oku kulandelayo: Kuphuculwe ukufikeleleka kwaye
ngendlela yohambo ngebhayisekile ukususela kubume bakalokunje obusi-1% ukuya kwi-8% ngo-
2030 apho kuyakuthi kubeligalelo ekucuthweni kwengxinano nokukhutshwa kweegesi kwimizi-mveliso
engolisa umoya. IKapa (xa kusiyiwa
emisebenzini) ngokujoliswe kwiihambo zommandla zabahambi ngokuphakathi komgama oli-10 km
ukuya kwi-15 km kwakhona neehambo eziqhutywa njengakumdibaniselwano wendlela
ngokwexesha elifutshane ukuya kwelisembindini.
isicwangciso-buchule esingohambo seSixeko saseKapa siyakuthi sikhokele imigaqo-nkqubo, iinkqubo
neeprojekthi ezithi ziphendule iimfuno zakalokunje nezandayo zezabahambi ngebhayisekile kwaye
zixhase ukukhula okuqhubekekayo kohambo ngebhayisekile ukuba ibeyindlela ephambili yezothutho
loluntu. Isicwangciso-buchule kufuneka siphengululwe kwaye sihlaziywe ubuncikane rhoqo emva
ngokuHlangeneyo (TITP) kwaye sihlale sihambelana notshintsho kucwangciso lokusingqongileyo
neemfuno zabasebenzisi baso.
